ari\">Ghiscari</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Patrimony_of_Hyrkoon\" title=\"Patrimony of Hyrkoon\">Hyrkoon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jogos_Nhai\" title=\"Jogos Nhai\">Jogos Nhai</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lhazareen\" title=\"Lhazareen\">Lhazareen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Qaathi\" title=\"Qaathi\">Qaathi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Shadow_Men\" title=\"Shadow Men\">Shadow Men</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Thousand_Islands\" title=\"Thousand Islands\">Thousand Islanders</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Valyrians\" title=\"Valyrians\">Valyrians</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">YiTish</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Sea\" title=\"Summer Sea\">Summer</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jade_Sea\" title=\"Jade Sea\">Jade Seas</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Islanders</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Naath\" title=\"Naath\">Naathi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lengii\" title=\"Lengii\">Lengii</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Shivering_Sea\" title=\"Shivering Sea\">Shivering Sea</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Ibbenese\" title=\"Ibbenese\">Ibbenese</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Thousand_Islands\" title=\"Thousand Islands\">Thousand Islanders</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limi